 <span data-ttu-id="59289-170">El objeto devuelto por la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CurrencyManager.List%2A> propiedad se puede convertir a cualquier tipo que implementa el <xref:System.Collections.IList> interfaz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-170">The object returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CurrencyManager.List%2A> property can be cast to any type that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IList> interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59289-171">Esto se usarán generalmente cuando sepa el tipo de la lista subyacente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-171">This will be commonly used when you know the type of the underlying list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59289-172">Por ejemplo, si están enlazados a datos a un <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, la lista subyacente es un <xref:System.Data.DataView> (que implementa <xref:System.Collections.IList>).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-172">For example, if you are data-bound to a <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, the underlying list is a <xref:System.Data.DataView> (which implements <xref:System.Collections.IList>).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59289-173">Otras clases que implementan la interfaz (no es una lista completa) incluyen <xref:System.Array>, <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>, y <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-173">Other classes that implement the interface (this is not a complete list) include <xref:System.Array>, <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>, and <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="59289-174">Cómo usar el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CurrencyManager.List%2A> propiedad depende de la clase que implementa el <xref:System.Collections.IList> interfaz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-174">How you use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CurrencyManager.List%2A> property depends on the class that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IList> interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59289-175">Por ejemplo, puede usar el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CurrencyManager.List%2A> propiedad para determinar el nombre de la lista.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-175">For example, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CurrencyManager.List%2A> property to determine the name of the list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59289-176">Si el origen de datos implementa la <xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypedList> interfaz, puede usar el <xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypedList.GetListName%2A> método para devolver el nombre de la tabla actual.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-176">If the data source implements the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypedList> interface, you can use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypedList.GetListName%2A> method to return the name of the current table.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59289-177">Esto se muestra en el siguiente código de C#:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59289-177">This is shown in the C# code below:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void PrintCurrentListName(DataGrid myDataGrid){   
   CurrencyManager myCM = (CurrencyManager)   
   BindingContext[myDataGrid.DataSource, myDataGrid.DataMember];   
   IList myList = myCM.List;   
   ITypedList thisList = (ITypedList) myList;   
   Console.WriteLine(thisList.GetListName(null));   
}  
```  
  
   
  
